<P>
 * As the story of our latest earthquake unfolded I couldn't help but wonder 
how long it would take Assembly Speaker Willie Brown to suggest a new increase 
in the sales tax. What a surprise -- with all that media covering the 
earthquake, he gets on the news with the proposal in less than 12 hours! 
</P>
