 * A day of terror, a night of fear. No power, no water, no food. Sirens blare, 
explosions blast. Somewhere a child calls for help while you wait for your home 
to collapse. An earthquake in Los Angeles, to be sure, but every day in Bosnia. 
</P>
<P>
 Isn't it time we helped those people? 
</P>
<P>
 JAY RUBIN 
