 In the Olympic League: 
</P>
<P>
 Cerritos Valley Christian 82, Orange Lutheran 48 -- Jodi Parriott of Cerritos 
Valley Christian (16-2, 6-0) scored 47 points, including the last 12 of the 
game. She re-entered the game late in the fourth quarter so she could break the 
school single-game scoring record. Amy Howard scored 12 points for Orange 
Lutheran (8-9, 2-4). 
</P>
<P>
 Capistrano Valley Christian 48, Ontario Christian 41 -- Andie Shaffner scored 
22 points for Capistrano Valley Christian (9-7, 3-3). Kari Systsma scored 14 
for Ontario Christian (9-7, 2-4). 
