 Valencia 53, Anaheim 28 -- Cindi Judd scored 15 points and LaQuinta Alexander 
added 14 points and 12 rebounds for Valencia (8-7, 3-2). 
</P>
<P>
 In the Pacific Coast League: 
</P>
<P>
