Lurmann added 13 for visiting Costa Mesa (11-6, 5-0), which took over sole 
possession of first place. Sarah Warnick had 14 points for Trabuco Hills 
(10-10, 4-1). 
</P>
<P>
 Laguna Hills 52, Century 37 -- Center Tayyiba Haneef scored 13 of her team's 
