game-high 22 points. Addie Alexander had 12 points and Nina Alexander added 11 
for Century (10-8, 1-4). 
</P>
<P>
 Estancia 57, Laguna Beach 18 -- Laura Czingula had 17 points and 11 rebounds 
and Jenny Drake added 13 points and nine steals for Estancia (14-3, 3-2).  
</P>
