<DOCNO> LA012194-0158 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 005931 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 21, 1994, Friday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
